Title: Nu-Way photo cell (MZ770S)
Description: This Nuway Satronic MZ770S photocell is an oil burner safety device, designed to monitor the combustion chamber for a flame signal. The photocell provides a monitored feedback signal back to the PCB and during start-up process ensures ignition happens only where there isn't a flame or stray light in the chamber. Once the flame it lit, the photocell continues monitoring, telling the PCB to initiate burner lock out if the flame is lost. This photocell is compatible with a wise selection of appliances including those in the Ecoflam, Stirling and ROL and NOL ranges.
